headline: Makers of HORMEL® SQUARE TABLE® Brand Dive Deeper into Chicken with Two New Bold Flavors
summary: Heat-and-eat meal solutions continue to gain traction among today's consumers, as more people seek hassle-free, easy-to-prepare options that deliver on taste and quality. This is no secret to the makers of the HORMEL® SQUARE TABLE® brand, who are tapping into that demand with the launch of two new chicken varieties: HORMEL® SQUARE TABLE® Tuscan Style Chicken and HORMEL® SQUARE TABLE® Maple Bourbon Chicken.
